data.description: Love summer pool days? Look no further! This home is perfect for large gatherings considering its sitting on a double lot approximately .5 acres! Let's not forget there are SO many upgrades! This custom built home has been lovingly taken care of and maintained including: Salt water pool, custom window treatments, new carpet, HVAC less than 2 years old. Trane whole house generator, brand new 90 gal hybrid water heater, 3 yr old deck, 1 yr old hot tub, camera security system, toilets have all been replaced, and you still have walk in attic space that could be finished! Roof was inspected in 2022. Schedule your showing today!
